  "Steven Roth is chairman and CEO of real estate investment trust Vornado Realty Trust.",
  "Vornado owns more than 20 million square feet of Manhattan office and retail space, plus properties in San Francisco and Chicago.",
  "Vornado owns two buildings alongside Donald Trump: 1290 Avenue of the Americas in New York City and 555 California Street in San Francisco.",
  "Roth served as an economic advisor to Trump's 2016 campaign, and was tapped for a spot on the president's short-lived infrastructure council.",
  "His wife, Daryl, is a Broadway and off-Broadway producer."
